# ============================================================
# Dashboard — environment (ALL OPTIONAL)
# The dashboard is a static file and needs NONE of these to run.
# These only matter if you wire the optional sys-admin MCP server
# (.mcp.json) for emailing reports / Drive backup / sheet logging,
# or if a future profile pulls live data from an API.
# Copy this file to .env and fill in only what you use.
# ============================================================

# --- Optional: AI agent helper MCP (sys-admin) ---
# Paths to a sys-admin MCP server, if you use one.
SYSADMIN_ROOT=
MCP_ROOT=

# --- Optional: live data pulls (future profiles) ---
# SEO profile is hand-fed JSON by default. If you later automate fetches:
# GA4_PROPERTY_ID=
# GSC_SITE_URL=
# PAGESPEED_API_KEY=
# CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN=

# --- Optional: AI assist for an agent customizing the dashboard ---
# Only if you use an AI agent locally to edit/extend the dashboard.
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
# OPENAI_API_KEY=
